videos.description: Cal's Charlie Moore gets a screen and takes advantage with the lay-in.
videos.headline: Moore gets a little help for the layup

videos.description: Off a Stanford steal, Marcus Allen gets past a couple Cal defenders and lays it in.
videos.headline: Good defense leads to an athletic score in transition

videos.description: California's Ivan Rabb catches and slams an alley-oop from Charlie Moore.
videos.headline: Rabb catches and slams off a lob pass

videos.description: Cal's Ivan Rabb fights for a rebound, lays it in and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Rabb's great effort ends in a bucket and foul

videos.description: California's Ivan Rabb steals a pass, then gives to Jabari Bird who scores, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Rabb's great defensive plays sets up a score

videos.description: In transition, Grant Mullins tosses a long pass from beyond the arc to Jabari Bird who catches and dunks with two hands.
videos.headline: Bird catches and slams alley-oop

videos.description: Stanford's Michael Humphrey connects on  a 3-pointer as time expires in the first half, and the game heads to the half tied at 25.
videos.headline: Humphrey sinks a 3 as the buzzer sounds

videos.description: Marcus Allen steals a pass, misses the lay-in on the other end, but Josh Sharma is there for the put back.
videos.headline: Offense leads to defense for Stanford

videos.description: Stanford's Reid Travis goes coast-to-coast for the layup.
videos.headline: Travis goes behind the back in transition to score

videos.description: Cal's Sam Singer jumps into a passing lane for the steal, then has an easy lay-in on the other end.
videos.headline: Singer reads a pass and steals it away

videos.description: Long cross court pass from Charlie Moore ends in an Ivan Rabb two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Rabb puts an exclamation point on a great pass from Moore
